// @flow

import * as React from "react";
import Leaflet from 'leaflet';

import SimpleExample from "./leaflet/simple";
import { 
  Page, 
  Grid,
  Container, 
  GalleryCard, 
  Form, 
  Text,
  StatsCard,

} from "tabler-react";

import SiteWrapper from "./SiteWrapper.react";

import json from "./data/Gallery.Items";
// TODO:Add GalleryCardList component to avoid insert extra className
// TODO:Update Page.Header to additional components

Leaflet.Icon.Default.imagePath =
  '//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/leaflet/1.3.4/images/'

function SiteMonitoringPage(): React.Node {
  const options = (
    <React.Fragment>
      <Form.Select className="w-auto mr-2">
        <option value="asc">Newest</option>
        <option value="desc">Oldest</option>
      </Form.Select>
      <Form.Input icon="search" placeholder="Search photo" />
    </React.Fragment>
  );
  return (
    <SiteWrapper>
      <Page.Content title="Site Monitoring Data Viewer and Downloader">
      <Grid.Row>
        <Form.Group>
          <Form.StaticText>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit duis tristique sollicitudin nibh. Dolor morbi non arcu risus quis varius quam. Nunc congue nisi vitae suscipit tellus mauris. Tincidunt id aliquet risus feugiat in.
          </Form.StaticText>
        </Form.Group>
      </Grid.Row>
      <Grid.Row>
        <Grid.Col lg={6}>
          <Container>
            <SimpleExample>
            </SimpleExample>
          </Container>
        </Grid.Col>
        <Grid.Col lg={6}>
          <Form.Group label="Data Download Selection">
            <Form.Checkbox
              label="Monitoring Sites"
              name="example-radios"
              value="1"
            />
            <Form.Group>
              <Form.Radio
                label="Bolinao, Pangasinan"
                name="example-radios"
                value="option1"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                label="Manila Bay"
                name="example-radios"
                value="option2"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                label="Monitoring Site 3"
                name="example-radios"
                value="option3"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                checked
                disabled
                label="Monitoring Site 4"
                name="example-radios2"
                value="option4"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                checked
                disabled
                label="Monitoring Site 5"
                name="example-radios3"
                value="option4"
              />
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Checkbox
              label="Sensor Data"
              name="example-radios"
              value="2"
            />
            <Form.Group>
              <Form.Radio
                label="Temperature"
                name="example-radios"
                value="option1"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                label="Salinity"
                name="example-radios"
                value="option2"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                label="pH"
                name="example-radios"
                value="option3"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                checked
                disabled
                label="Dissolved Oxygen"
                name="example-radios2"
                value="option4"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                checked
                disabled
                label="Chlorophyll-a"
                name="example-radios3"
                value="option4"
              />
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Checkbox
              label="Biological Data"
              name="example-radios"
              value="3"
            />
            <Form.Group>
              <Form.Radio
                label="Toxicity"
                name="example-radios"
                value="option1"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                label="Species List"
                name="example-radios"
                value="option2"
              />
              <Form.Radio
                label="Predictive Model Results"
                name="example-radios"
                value="option3"
              />
            </Form.Group>
          </Form.Group>
        </Grid.Col>
      </Grid.Row>
      </Page.Content>
    </SiteWrapper>
  );
}

export default SiteMonitoringPage;
